<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink362">
<l>patukkait tāya votukkaruṅ kavalaic</l>
<l>ciṟukaṇ yāṉai yuṟupakai niṉaiyā</l>
<l>tiyāṅkuvan taṉaiyō pūntār mārpa</l>
<l>varuḷpuri neñca muyttara</l>
<l>viruḷpora niṉṟa viravi ṉāṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>O man with flower garland on [your] chest! </l>
<l>How did you come through the crossroads with piles of stones,  </l>
<l>where shelter is hard to find, </l>
<l>undeterred by the hostility of small-eyed elephants, </l>
<l>in the night that stands, </l>
<l>when grace-desiring heart dispells [it, but] darkness resists. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
